moduleMetadataJson.name: VxWorks WDB Agent Remote Memory Dump
moduleMetadataJson.description: This module provides the ability to dump the system memory of a VxWorks target through WDBRPC
author: hdm <x@hdm.io>

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: RHOSTS
options.description: The target host(s), range CIDR identifier, or hosts file with syntax 'file:<path>'

options.name: LPATH
options.description: The local filename to store the dumped memory

options.name: OFFSET
options.description: The starting offset to read the memory dump (hex allowed)
